TO INSTALL BREAKTHROUGH:-----1) Make sure you have an installed copy of WolfEdit 1.1 lying around on your hard drive.  NOTE: IF YOU ARE GOING TO BE INSTALLING BREAKTHROUGH INTO A FIRST ENCOUNTER COPY OF WOLF3D, YOU SHOULD NOT USE WOLFEDIT 1.1A.  IF YOU DO, BAD THINGS MIGHT HAPPEN.2) Double-click the Breakthrough icon.  WolfEdit should open and a level window should appear.3) Choose 'Install...' from the File menu.4) Find and select your copy of Wolf3d.5) Quit WolfEdit and launch Wolf3d.6) Kill some Nazis!AJT